{"tid":1301607,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【總結經驗】77遊行向中國遊客宣傳其實效果唔錯","createTime":"2019-07-09T16:36:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T17:02:57.000Z","uid":36901,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"65526d28732e4e93a81a79483c73c79382e0ba65","tid":1301607,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:36:37.000Z","msg":"一點當天見聞，覺得可供日後參考<br />\n<br />\n1.語言好重要，用普通話向強國人講解逃犯條例,警察開槍打學生，佢見你用普通話，多數都願意聽下，好多真係唔知乜事。<br />\n<br />\n2.強國人比想像中好奇，要好好趁機解釋，現實唔係個個都係小粉紅黎<br />\n<br />\n3.歌聲好重要，中港城唱義勇軍進行曲，喊普通話口號真是唔錯，我懷疑直接唱海闊天空對強國人(後生個批)都work<br />\n<br />\n4.笑容好重要，甚至遊行中揮下手都有助減少敵意。<br />\n<br />\n5.統戰(即係 we connect)，係共產黨起家三大法寶之一，要長期抗爭，一定要學好呢門絕學。"},{"pid":"335a64eb17efeade2d8d32c9855786bb3115dc25","tid":1301607,"uid":200758,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:38:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AiR3F8V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAiR3F8V.jpg&h=f4a2740b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EuDmAd2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEuDmAd2.jpg&h=28455d55&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7836345348b8aa84e79cfa72580674c697ee13ef","tid":1301607,"uid":36901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"335a64eb17efeade2d8d32c9855786bb3115dc25","tid":1301607,"uid":200758,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:38:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AiR3F8V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAiR3F8V.jpg&h=f4a2740b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EuDmAd2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEuDmAd2.jpg&h=28455d55&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:47:06.000Z","msg":"714 會經新城市附近<br />\n都幾肯定會有遊客八掛<br />\n雖然今次係五大訴求重點<br />\n但遇上遊客不妨友善宣傳講解<br />\n唔好放過任何統戰機會"},{"pid":"fe3b9fd064cdbf789dd15653e799fd0afc4098bd","tid":1301607,"uid":276507,"like